      <title>本周全球大宗商品值得关注的五张图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉比卡咖啡的价格正接近十多年来的最高水平。8 月份油价波动，交易员们正准备迎接年底可能出现的动荡。大豆、玉米和小麦的大量供应也拖累了谷物相对于其他商品的走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
